233 payment out of said fund of an amount less than the actual loss or
234 damages incurred by the owner or less than the order of restitution
235 awarded by the commissioner or the Superior Court. In no event shall
236 any payment out of said guaranty fund be in excess of twenty-five
237 thousand dollars for any single claim by an owner.
238 (m) If the money deposited in the guaranty fund is insufficient to
